=== 認知療法 ===
在對抑鬱症患者的研究後，他發現病人們擁有自發產生負面思緒的經歷。<ref name="att">{{cite web|title=Automatic Thoughts in CBT (Part 2)|url=https://beckinstitute.org/blog/automatic-thoughts-in-cbt-part-2/|accessdate=November 1, 2021|date=June 8, 2021|publisher=Beck Institute|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102055607/https://beckinstitute.org/blog/automatic-thoughts-in-cbt-part-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>貝克把這些認知稱作“自動思維”，並且發現這些思緒內容分為三類：關於自身、世界及未來的負面想法。他認為這種認知是像[[憂鬱認知三角|憂鬱認知三角]]一樣相互聯繫的。<ref name="att" />花費在反應出自動思維的不多時間使得病人認為這些想法是有根據、可信的。<ref name="past and future2">{{cite journal|title=The Past and the future of Cognitive Therapy|url=http://jppr.psychiatryonline.org/cgi/reprint/6/4/276.pdf|last=Beck|first=Aaron|journal=Journal of Psychotherapy Practice and Research|issue=4|year=1996|volume=6|pages=276–284|pmc=3330473|pmid=9292441|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215210611/http://jppr.psychiatryonline.org/cgi/reprint/6/4/276.pdf|url-status=dead|archive-date=December 15, 2011|access-date=June 7, 2011}}</ref>

貝克開始幫助病人識別和評估這些想法，藉由這樣的方法，病人有辦法更現實地思考，使得他們能夠更好的情緒感受並有更正常的行為表現。他在CBT中發展了關鍵想法，解釋了不同的[[心理障礙|心理障礙]]和不同種類的認知扭曲有關。<ref name="past and future2" />他發現，無論何種心理障礙，認知扭曲都對我們的行為有負面影響。<ref name="past and future2" />貝克解釋，成功的介入會教育一個人去了解並察覺到他們的認知扭曲，以及如何去挑戰其影響。<ref name="past and future2" /> 他發現到頻繁的自動思維揭示了一個人的核心信念。他解釋說，核心信念是由整個人生經歷所形成的；我們“感覺”這些信念是真實的。<ref name="past and future2" />

自那時起，貝克和他在全球同事在研究了這種形式的心理治療在治療多種疾病上的療效，包括憂鬱症，[[躁鬱症|双相情感障碍]]，[[进食障碍|進食障礙]]，[[物質濫用|物質濫用]]，[[焦虑症|焦慮症]]，[[人格障礙|人格障礙]]和其他諸多具有心理學因素的醫療狀況。<ref name="past and future">{{cite journal|title=The Past and the future of Cognitive Therapy|url=http://jppr.psychiatryonline.org/cgi/reprint/6/4/276.pdf|last=Beck|first=Aaron|journal=Journal of Psychotherapy Practice and Research|issue=4|year=1996|volume=6|pages=276–284|pmc=3330473|pmid=9292441|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215210611/http://jppr.psychiatryonline.org/cgi/reprint/6/4/276.pdf|url-status=dead|archive-date=December 15, 2011|access-date=June 7, 2011}}</ref>認知療法也被成功的應用於焦慮症、[[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]]的個體。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cognitive behavioral therapy for schizophrenia|url=https://nyulangone.org/conditions/schizophrenia/treatments/cognitive-behavioral-therapy-for-schizophrenia|access-date=March 20, 2021|website=NYU Langone Health|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108062721/https://nyulangone.org/conditions/schizophrenia/treatments/cognitive-behavioral-therapy-for-schizophrenia|dead-url=no}}</ref>他還專注於精神分裂症、[[边缘性人格障碍|邊緣性人格障礙]]以及曾反复自殺未遂患者的認知治療。<ref>{{cite web|title=Validation for Patients with Borderline Personality Disorder|url=https://beckinstitute.org/blog/validation-for-patients-with-borderline-personality-disorder/|accessdate=November 1, 2021|date=June 8, 2021|publisher=Back Institute|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102154643/https://beckinstitute.org/blog/validation-for-patients-with-borderline-personality-disorder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 相關组织 ==
貝克參與[[宾夕法尼亚大学|賓夕法尼亞大學]]的研究，並在貝克學會為區域精神病學住院醫生、研究生以及心理健康專業人士進行兩週一次的案例會議。<ref>{{Cite web|title=World-Class Facilities {{!}} Beck Institute for Cognitive Behavior Therapy|url=http://www.beckinstitute.org/beck-institute-facilities/|access-date=March 19, 2018|date=January 29, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129101443/http://www.beckinstitute.org/beck-institute-facilities/|archive-date=January 29, 2012}}</ref>他在2007年被選為[[美国文理科学院|美國文理科學院]]院士。<ref name="AAAS">{{cite web|title=Book of Members, 1780–2010: Chapter B|url=http://www.amacad.org/publications/BookofMembers/ChapterB.pdf|access-date=May 29, 2011|publisher=American Academy of Arts and Sciences|archive-date=2006-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060618085806/http://www.amacad.org/publications/BookofMembers/ChapterB.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

貝克是非營利組織{{Link-en|贝克认知行为疗法研究所|Beck Institute for Cognitive Behavior Therapy}}的創辦人及名譽主席，以及精神病理學研究中心（Psychopathology Research Center, PRC）的主任，該中心是{{Link-en|自殺行為治療及研究中心|Center for the Prevention of Suicide}}的母組織。<ref name=":0" />1986年，他曾為[[牛津大学|牛津大學]]的訪問學者。<ref name="Grawemeyer" />

從1992年起，貝克擔任美國賓夕法尼亞州大學的名譽教授，<ref name=":0" />以及[[天普大學|天普大學]]和{{Link-en|紐澤西藥學暨牙科醫學大學|University of Medicine and Dentistry of New Jersey}}的兼職教授。<ref name="Grawemeyer" />

== 个人生活 ==
贝克于1950年与菲利斯·W·贝克结婚，他们共有四个孩子：罗伊、朱迪、丹和爱丽丝。<ref name="Beck2" />菲利斯是宾夕法尼亚联邦上诉法院的第一位女法官。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Faculty Details|url=http://marinolegalcle.com/faculties/facultydetail/258|access-date=March 19, 2018|date=September 29, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929093758/http://marinolegalcle.com/faculties/facultydetail/258|archive-date=September 29, 2015}}</ref>她的小女儿爱丽丝·贝克·杜博也是同一法院的法官，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Judge Alice Beck Dubow | Superior Court Judges | Superior Court | Courts | Unified Judicial System of Pennsylvania|url=http://www.pacourts.us/courts/superior-court/superior-court-judges/judge-alice-beck-dubow|access-date=2021-11-08|archive-date=2021-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117023019/https://www.pacourts.us/courts/superior-court/superior-court-judges/judge-alice-beck-dubow|dead-url=no}}</ref>而大女儿朱迪思是一位著名的以行为认知疗法而出名的心理学家，她撰写了该领域的基本文章，并且是贝克研究所的联合创始人。<ref name="beckins">[https://beckinstitute.org/about-beck/] {{Wayback|url=https://beckinstitute.org/about-beck/ |date=20210612002634 }}, ''Beck Institute for Cognitive Behavior Therapy'', Bala Cynwyd, PA: Beck Institute for Cognitive Behavior Therapy, 2014, Retrieved February 21, 2014.</ref>他于2021年7月18日年满100岁，并于当年的11月1日在他位于费城的家中在睡梦中去世。<ref>{{cite web|title=100 anni di Beck: un acrobata tra cognitivismo e psicoanalisi – Monografia|url=https://www.stateofmind.it/2021/07/100-anni-aaron-t-beck-monografia/|accessdate=September 11, 2021|date=July 17, 2021|publisher=State of Mind|language=it|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104221432/https://www.stateofmind.it/2021/07/100-anni-aaron-t-beck-monografia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{Cite news|last=Carey|first=Benedict|date=November 1, 2021|title=Dr. Aaron T. Beck, Developer of Cognitive Therapy, Dies at 100|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/11/01/health/dr-aaron-t-beck-dead.html|access-date=November 1, 2021|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053917/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/11/01/health/dr-aaron-t-beck-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Obituaries|first=Telegraph|date=November 1, 2021|title=Aaron Beck, psychiatrist whose development of cognitive behavioural therapy transformed millions of lives around the world – obituary|language=en-GB|work=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2021/11/01/aaron-beck-psychiatrist-whose-development-cognitive-behavioural/|access-date=November 1, 2021|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111162348/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2021/11/01/aaron-beck-psychiatrist-whose-development-cognitive-behavioural/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://getindianews.com/how-did-dr-aaron-beck-die-and-what-was-his-cause-of-death-developer-of-cognitive-therapy-dies-at-100/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-08 |archive-date=2021-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105120818/https://getindianews.com/how-did-dr-aaron-beck-die-and-what-was-his-cause-of-death-developer-of-cognitive-therapy-dies-at-100/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 心理量表 ==
除了[[貝克抑鬱量表|貝克抑鬱量表]]（BDI），貝克還開發了{{Link-en|貝克絕望量表|Beck Hopelessness Scale}}（BHS）<ref>Beck A.T. (1988). ''Beck Hopelessness Scale.'' San Antonio, TX: The Psychological Corporation.</ref>、貝克自殺意念量表（BSS）、{{Link-en|貝克焦慮量表|Beck Anxiety Inventory}}（BAI）、貝克兒童及青少年量表<ref>[http://www.beckinstitute.org/beck-inventory-and-scales/ "Beck Scales for Adults and Children"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beckinstitute.org/beck-inventory-and-scales/ |date=20151107183354 }} Beck Institute for Cognitive Therapy and Research. Retrieved January 11, 2007.</ref>、克拉克-贝克强迫症量表（CBOCI）<ref>{{cite web|title=Clark-Beck Obsessive-Compulsive Inventory|url=https://www.pearsonassessments.com/store/usassessments/en/Store/Professional-Assessments/Personality-%26-Biopsychosocial/Clark-Beck-Obsessive-Compulsive-Inventory/p/100000201.html|accessdate=November 1, 2021|publisher=Pearson|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102145833/https://www.pearsonassessments.com/store/usassessments/en/Store/Professional-Assessments/Personality-%26-Biopsychosocial/Clark-Beck-Obsessive-Compulsive-Inventory/p/100000201.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及医学患者的BDI-快速筛查<ref>{{cite web|title=BDI - FastScreen for Medical Patients|url=https://www.pearsonassessments.com/store/usassessments/en/Store/Professional-Assessments/Personality-%26-Biopsychosocial/Brief/BDI---FastScreen-for-Medical-Patients/p/100000173.html|accessdate=November 1, 2021|publisher=Pearson|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104235251/https://www.pearsonassessments.com/store/usassessments/en/Store/Professional-Assessments/Personality-%26-Biopsychosocial/Brief/BDI---FastScreen-for-Medical-Patients/p/100000173.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝克合作過的心理學家{{Link-en|瑪麗亞·科瓦奇|Maria Kovacs}}開發的{{Link-en|兒童抑鬱量表|Children's Depression Inventory}}，即採用了BDI的一種模式。<ref>Kovacs, M. (1992).  ''Children's Depression Inventory.''  North Tonawanda, NY: Multi-Health Systems, Inc.</ref><ref>Kovacs, M., & Beck, A.T. (1977).  "An empirical-clinical approach toward a definition of childhood depression."  In Schulterbrandt, J.G., & Raskin, A. (Eds.).  ''Depression in children: Diagnosis, treatment, and concept models.''  New York, NY: Raven.</ref>

